<div class="title">Fond of the Drink</div>
<div class="substance">Alcohol</div>
<div class="author">by <a href="/experiences/exp.cgi?A=Search&AuthorSearch=foolish&Exact=1">foolish</a></div>


<div class="ts-citation">Citation:&nbsp;&nbsp; foolish. "Fond of the Drink: An Experience with Alcohol (exp21502)". <u>Erowid.org</u>. Feb 24, 2003. erowid.org/exp/21502</div>

